@startuml
title 项目保存与重新打开 - 时序图

actor "操作者" as User
participant "MainWindow" as UI
participant "FileDialog" as Dialog
participant "ProjectActions" as Actions
participant "ProjectSessionMapper" as Mapper
participant "ProjectRepository" as Repository
participant "ProjectSessionRestorer" as Restorer
participant "运行态状态" as Runtime
participant "文件系统" as FS

User -> UI: 保存项目
UI -> Dialog: SaveProject()
Dialog --> UI: selected path
UI -> Actions: saveProject(path, calibration,\nmeasurements, dyes, channels,\nedfOptions, stitchSearchPercent)
Actions -> Mapper: toDocument(session state)
Mapper --> Actions: ProjectDocument
Actions -> Repository: save(path, document)
Repository -> FS: write *.cvproj
FS --> Repository: ok
Repository --> Actions: ok
Actions --> UI: ProjectActionResult(saved)
UI --> User: 显示保存状态

User -> UI: 打开项目
UI -> Dialog: OpenProject()
Dialog --> UI: selected path
UI -> Actions: loadProject(path)
Actions -> Repository: load(path)
Repository -> FS: read *.cvproj
FS --> Repository: content
Repository --> Actions: ProjectDocument
Actions -> Mapper: fromDocument(document)
Mapper --> Actions: ProjectSessionState
Actions --> UI: ProjectActionResult(loaded)
UI -> Restorer: restore(runtime, sessionState)
Restorer -> Runtime: apply calibration, measurements,\ndyes, channels and processing settings
Restorer -> Runtime: clear old processing queues,\nresults and retry snapshots
Restorer --> UI: ProjectSessionRestoreResult
UI --> User: 刷新面板、列表和预览

@enduml
